results.name: Benchmark ESG Pvt Limited India
results.summary: Benchmark ESG provides a comprehensive cloud-based platform for organizations to manage Environment, Health, and Safety (EHS), sustainability reporting, and operational risk. Their tools enable businesses to automate compliance processes, track disclosure metrics, and leverage data analytics for ESG performance.

results.name: Hanunnotech (Hanumayamma Innovations and Technologies Pvt. Ltd.)
results.summary: Hanunnotech specializes in AI-powered monitoring solutions and wearable IoT sensors designed for livestock management, specialty crops, and small-to-mid-size farms. The company utilizes data analytics and predictive modeling to help farmers and financial institutions optimize productivity, mitigate climate risks, and enhance agricultural supply chain certainty.

results.name: Sol9X Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Sol9X Pvt. Ltd. architects secure, mission-critical AI solutions and digital infrastructure for high-stakes industries like defense and manufacturing. The company integrates Edge AI, Digital Twin simulations, and IoT-driven automation to enhance real-time operational intelligence and security.

results.name: Rooman Technologies Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Rooman Technologies is a professional training provider that offers certification programs and vocational courses in networking, software, and hardware. The company partners with government agencies and academic institutions to deliver employability-focused upskilling and reskilling programs across India.
key_offerings: IT Certification Training (Cisco, Microsoft, Red Hat)

results.name: Rapifuzz Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Rapifuzz Pvt. Ltd. focuses on simplifying cybersecurity by providing tailored solutions and proactive guidance for organizations. They specialize in integrating security early into the DevSecOps process to help companies enhance their overall protection and make informed security decisions.

results.name: Virtual Height IT Services Pvt. Ltd.
Minaions Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Minaions Pvt. Ltd. offers an AI-driven platform specifically designed to automate the creation of tender documents and streamline bid management workflows. The technology helps organizations enhance their procurement efficiency by simplifying the complex process of responding to government and corporate tenders.

results.name: Kenpath technologies Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Kenpath Technologies provides full-stack AI engineering and cloud stack development designed to operate at a population scale for governments and enterprises. They manage the entire lifecycle of intelligent systems, from strategic discovery and PoC to large-scale deployment and SaaS support.

results.name: T4G Lab
results.summary: T4G Lab is a digital product studio that partners with startups and non-profit organizations to build technology-driven solutions for social impact. The company develops a range of products, from advanced AI tools to simple digital applications, designed to solve pressing global challenges.

results.name: Gazelle Information Technologies
results.summary: Gazelle is a leading reCommerce platform that facilitates the buying and selling of pre-owned consumer electronics such as smartphones, tablets, and laptops. The company provides a streamlined trade-in process with instant quotes and sells certified pre-owned devices to consumers seeking cost-effective hardware alternatives.

results.name: Sambanova Systems India Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: SambaNova Systems provides a full-stack AI platform that integrates custom-designed hardware with optimized software to power large-scale foundation models and generative AI. The company enables enterprises to deploy high-performance AI infrastructure that serves as a technology backbone for complex machine learning workloads.

results.name: Soket Labs Technology and Research Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Soket Labs is an Indian AI research firm dedicated to developing indigenous large language models specifically optimized for Indic languages. The company focuses on building foundational AI infrastructure to advance the pursuit of ethical Artificial General Intelligence.

results.name: Prismberry Technologies Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Prismberry Technologies is a Noida-based IT services firm specializing in software engineering, cloud solutions, and data analytics. The company is currently expanding its footprint in the artificial intelligence sector through the launch of specialized AI products and enterprise-grade tech solutions.

results.name: NIMBORA
results.summary: Nimbora is a water intelligence platform that provides real-time monitoring and analytics to optimize water usage. The platform helps enterprises identify leaks and inefficiencies to promote resource conservation and reduce operational costs.

results.name: Protean International DMCC
results.summary: Protean International specializes in conceptualizing and deploying population-scale digital public infrastructure and e-governance solutions globally. Leveraging over 25 years of experience with the Indian government, the company provides mission-critical systems for identity management, taxation, and social security implementation.
key_offerings: Digital Public Infrastructure (DPI) & India Stack Solutions

results.name: YuVerse
results.summary: YuVerse provides high-speed internet and wireless telecommunications services, specializing in mobile connectivity and residential broadband solutions. The company offers competitive data plans, trade-in incentives for flagship smartphones, and contract buyout programs for new subscribers.

results.name: ShellKode
results.summary: ShellKode is a cloud-native consultancy that assists organizations in transitioning legacy systems to the cloud with a focus on data and cloud-native architectures. By integrating AI/ML and data analytics, they enable businesses to optimize their ROI and gain actionable insights through scalable enterprise solutions.

results.name: Vicharak Computers Pvt. Ltd.
results.summary: Vicharak Computers develops next-generation hardware based on reconfigurable computing to overcome the performance limitations of traditional Von Neumann architectures. Their technology allows hardware to adapt to software requirements in real-time using parallel processing to deliver high-efficiency performance for edge and cloud computing.

results.name: Suronex and Zero Forg
results.summary: Suronex provides a comprehensive cloud security platform that enables organizations to manage and mitigate risks while maintaining visibility and control across their digital environments. The company focuses on bridging the gap between rapid innovation and security by offering solutions for cloud compliance and proactive risk management.

results.name: TrueFan AI
results.summary: TrueFan is an engagement platform that connects fans with Indian superstars through personalized video messages won via gamified movie quizzes. The company also leverages AI video technology to provide scalable celebrity engagement solutions for enterprises.

results.name: Avinyaa EdTech (Kreativespace)
results.summary: Avinyaa EdTech develops an AI-driven ecosystem designed to enhance learning productivity and accessibility for students and educators. The company offers a suite of tools including AI writing assistants, interactive tutors that convert multimedia into study materials, and a comprehensive Learning Management System.
